				<main role="main"><article class="main-content-home"><h1 class="home"><span>Blanket Independent School District</span></h1>
<div class="pom-container"><h2 class="">Home of the Mighty Tigers</h2></div>
        <p class="">At Blanket ISD, it’s all about our students. We make it our business to know every student, and it’s our nature to care about every student. Despite our small size, we believe every member of the Blanket ISD family deserves access to the best education, resources, and extracurricular opportunities we can offer. We want our students to succeed.</p>
<div class="pom-container"><p class="">At Blanket, we know every child by name who attends our school. We are honored to provide educational services for our <a href="/Elementary" title="" alt="" target="_self">elementary</a> (PK–5), <a href="/Junior-High" title="" alt="" target="_self">junior high</a> (6–8), and <a href="/High-School" title="" alt="" target="_self">high school</a> (9–12) students.</p></div>
        <h2 class="">From Our Superintendent</h2>
        <p class="">Welcome to Blanket ISD, where we are a family of dedicated teachers, administrators, and support personnel whose highest priority is to ensure all of our students are inspired and equipped to pursue a future beyond what they can imagine. That’s not just a mission statement—it’s a way of life that reminds us daily of why we do what we do.</p>
<div class="pom-container">
<p class="">Our students’ achievements are many, and we are extremely proud of every state, region, and district honor they earn. But we are also proud of every milestone and progressive step that our students take in their own educational journey. We recognize our community and parents as our most valued partners, and together, we will continue to strive for student success at every level. I invite you to browse our website and reach out to our district personnel if you have questions about Blanket ISD.</p>
<div class="pom-container">
<p class="">Thank you for this opportunity to serve Blanket ISD.</p>
<div class="pom-container">
<p class="signature">David Whisenhunt</p>
<div class="pom-container"><p class="">David Whisenhunt<br>Superintendent</p></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
